Polytraits,is,a,database,of,biological,traits,of,polychaetes,bristle,worms,including,information,about,morphological,behavioral,reproductive,and,larval,characteristics,collected,from,the,literature,The,polytraits,database,is,exposed,through,a,REST,API,consisting,of,two,methods,The,taxon,method,searches,a,taxon,name,and,returns,corresponding,identifiers,The,traits,method,retrieve,traits,information,for,taxon,identifiers